{"tid":619980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"48歲港熟女與支那藉20歲男友鬧分手開拖驚動警員消防到場","createTime":"2018-04-07T07:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T13:58:31.000Z","uid":39539,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"afbe212a0a3a4e0f55d020883117e714120bb75f","tid":619980,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:20:19.000Z","msg":"黃大仙一對母子戀情侶鬧分手反鎖屋內爭執，驚動警方到場。現場為瓊東街8號嘉峰臺5座一單位，一名48歲姓吳女住客，早前結識一名年僅20歲姓張的內地男友，對方於本月3日持雙程證來港探望，今早10時許，吳女發現300元現金失去，懷疑遭人偷走，擬拿取男友銀包查看，惟張拒絕並提出分手，更要求立即離開。吳女不答充，雙方發生爭執，張男突爬窗企圖離去，吳女趨前制止，糾纏間遭人追打，腳部受傷，連忙退回房間躲避。大廈看更發現有人爬出窗門，立即報案。 <br />\n<br />\n警員接報聯同消防人員趕至，進入單位調查，初步相信是情侶糾紛，吳女由救護車送院治理。而張男涉嫌偷竊及傷人被捕，再帶署扣查。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/152013_c85cc4c7df9be88a70dada5e5540a36d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F152013_c85cc4c7df9be88a70dada5e5540a36d.png&h=ca9f722d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d565f06a56649c8e29eadbaf0c7391d2c9dcad3","tid":619980,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"為左300爬窗走<br />\n一個唔小心跌落街<br />\n幾撚咁無謂"},{"pid":"6da0e2a33caf0d32579917d3323dec85cc71870a","tid":619980,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c223ecfff9d58c5d9fb9758ee99f61665a62c785","tid":619980,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTVB啲低能劇噉"},{"pid":"15990afd7edc8e77851e820bb621774daa6c2a0a","tid":619980,"uid":179378,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"吳小姐 我頂上做你男朋友得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見字請回<img src=\"/assets/f